\n\"Ket\"]\)", 
  "\!\(\*TemplateBox[{\nSubscriptBox[\"y\", \"-\"]},\n\"Ket\"]\)"}, 
 BlochVector@*Normalize /@ Eigenvectors[PauliMatrix[2]]]
```

